volunteer_experiences.description:
The broad objective for the members of the A&O Fund Graphic Media Sector consists of:
The provision of education activities for employees and potential employees in the graphics sector;
Carrying out activities in the field of the labor market in the graphic sector, including stimulating the supply of employees in the graphic sector;
Obtaining and co-financing national and international eligible activities on previous points.


The objectives of the A&O Fonds Grafimediabranche endeavors to achieve the foundation by:
Giving courses or having courses in the field of graphic media;
Giving subsidies to organizations that provide courses or education in the field of graphic media;
Providing information to interested parties in the field of graphic media;
Conducting advertising campaigns, organizing and conducting workshops and lectures in the field of graphic media;
Taking care of grant applications for national and international subsidies by the organization itself, for the member organizations and for the members / employees of the member organizations.
